reviewText: I saw poop at family values and I'll make sure to buy it soon.  Limp Bizkit is awesome and it's cool to see all their friends and hear their  stories from them.  Fred is a great director and this video is just more  proof.  If you're a person who only likes 'faith' and 'nookie' or only  likes LB because fred is sooo hot then this isn't for you, but otherwise  get it.
